data.description: ABSOLUTELY PRIME LOT AND LOCATION! Perched on a .78 acre lot directly across the street from Cooks Bay & multi-million dollar lakefronts, this 2600 sq foot home has room for everyone. There have been a number of significant updates to the home, incl a full BSMT bath remodel, partial UL bath remodel, new paint throughout much of the home, new outlet covers, new fencing, etc... (full list of updates available in supplements). Enjoy 3 spacious bedrooms on one level including a private primary w/ 3/4 bath (bathroom awaiting your finishing touches).  The yard is TO DIE FOR!  There is an inground pool, perfect for hot summer days, a workshop, a plethora of fruit trees, and plenty of space for all your toys.  Enjoy living w/in walking distance to schools, restaurants & bars, swim beaches, parks, trails, shopping & so much more! This is your chance to get into the Westonka area near the lake at a price you can afford! Schedule your showing today!
